26/11/2004
SOFIA, Bulgaria -- Journalists from 160 national and regional press, electronic and online media signed the Media Ethics Code on Thursday (25 November). 
The move aims to support the local media in its bid for journalistic independence and to encourage improvements in professional standards. 
It also sets special rules for using information supplied by unidentified sources. 
(Mediapool, bTV - 26/11/04)
